txt.en: 'I will ready our troops, Ilzk창l. Igash's devoted will fall to my blade and we will claim their tribute for the White Hand!'
'Best that you remember that, lest you find yourself cast into the deep dark.'
'Even if we fail, our insurrection will never be learned, thanks to your corpses.'
'Curs and wretches? Remember, uruk... you are a guest of the Gazathrug.'
'Come creatures, come and face your death, face your fear... face me.'
'Listen well to your brethren, or you shall learn the true meaning of fear.'
Hold your tongue, maggot, or you will raise my ire and force my hand.'
'Your folly may yet bring us glory! See that these curs are slain.'
'It is not yet time, Ilzk창l!'
'You have ten minutes.'
'Ha ha ha, whelps.'
'I will ready our troops, Ilzk창l. Igash's devoted will fall to my blade, and his tribute shall be taken for the White Hand!'
'The White Hand tires of this ruse. The time is at hand, Nardur! You will know the meaning of terror!'
'Silence, you pathetic worms!'
'Feed me your fear!'
'You worry too much, Nardur - what is this?'
'Fool! Shark청 will have our heads for this! Now, we must attack these Orcs.'
'Go now, Nardur! Make ready for battle! Moria will fall to the White Hand!'
'Look here, Nardur: spittle licking Warg-riders, worthless wretches riding curs.'
'You see the intruders, Nardur. Ready our forces.'
'I will deal with these new curs. Ready our forces and make war on Moria if I do not arrive in ten minutes time!'
